# ðŸš€ Project Management Tool

A full-stack Project Management Tool similar to Jira, built using React (frontend), Node.js/Express (backend), MongoDB (database), and Tailwind CSS. The app supports real-time project collaboration, role-based access (Admin, Project Manager, User), project/task tracking, dark mode, deadline timelines, and charts for visualizing progress.

---

## ðŸ§° Tech Stack

### Frontend:
- React
- Tailwind CSS (with Dark Mode)
- Axios
- Recharts (for progress graphs)
- React Router DOM

### Backend:
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB (Mongoose)
- JWT Authentication
- Role-based Authorization

---

## âœ¨ Features

- âœ… Register/Login with JWT tokens
- âœ… Role-based access (Admin, Project Manager, Team Lead, User)
- âœ… Create, update, delete projects
- âœ… Assign team members to projects
- âœ… Task management with priority, status, deadline
- âœ… Project progress chart using Recharts
- âœ… Timeline & dashboard view
- âœ… Dark mode toggle (Tailwind CSS)
- âœ… Error handling and token-based protection

